Player Assigned to the Field

(DND, Point and Click, Lineups Dropdown)
The starting lineup is now complete and the DMR status 'lineup' is not saved
This lineup  text needs to exist for the dmr buisness rule to be completed
Save 'lineup' to the DMR status via updatePlanningEvent

Player Removed from the Field

(Player Removal, Clear Field, Change Formation)
If the starting lineup WAS COMPLETE and is now INCOMPLETE as well as  the DMR status 'lineup' is saved
This lineup  text needs to be removed for the dmr buisness rule to be checked off
Remove 'lineup' from the DMR status via updatePlanningEvent
